#, fuzzy
msgid "https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[*1.0.0.Alpha1*] (January 2026) -- Aligned with the draft A2A 1.0 specification: migrated to Java records, switched from Jackson to Gson, introduced BOMs, and added comprehensive Javadoc."
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[1.0.0.Alpha1] (janeiro de 2026) - Alinhado com o rascunho da especificação A2A 1.0: migrou para registros Java, mudou de Jackson para Gson, introduziu BOMs e adicionou um Javadoc abrangente."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-18-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[*1.0.0.Alpha2*] (February 2026) -- Added OpenTelemetry-based telemetry, push notification support, and the streamlined `AgentEmitter` API."
msgstr "link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[1.0.0.Alpha2] (fevereiro de 2026) - Adicionada telemetria baseada em OpenTelemetry, suporte a notificações push e a API `AgentEmitter` simplificada."

